# Next.js

- App Router with route groups: `(auth)`, `(dashboard)`, onboarding.
- Server Components by default — add `'use client'` only when required.
- Clerk middleware protects dashboard routes.
- Metadata exported from layout.tsx and page.tsx.
- Transpile monorepo packages in next.config.js.
- Import global styles from `@jobos/ui/globals.css`.
